  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><h1 id=\"yVKWh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如何使用</span></h1><p id=\"u32eb42c1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">大纲不会自动生成，在正文中输入标题，标题内容即可在右侧大纲展示出来。</span></p><p id=\"u6ca80083\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"KDi98\"><span class=\"ne-text\">操作步骤</span></h2><p id=\"u87a82755\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">你可以先输入正文内容，选中正文内容，点击工具栏将正文内容设置为标题。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">将正文内容设置为标题后，标题会作为大纲在右侧空白处展示出来。如下图</span></p><p id=\"u1d3c1bce\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"><br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635927778848-feec1b0b-8a71-4d6b-93a6-4fef08592f92.png\" width=\"886\" id=\"ub38e81d2\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\"><br /><br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">同时也可以在行首输入快捷键</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">或者行内（mac 系统 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">command + /</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、windows 系统 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\"> ctrl+/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 设置好标题格式后，再编辑内容），快速设置标题。</span></p><p id=\"uadb0ea32\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\"><br /></span></strong><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635928968849-956d75fd-47ad-4ca3-8e3e-9e6a0aca87d2.png\" width=\"640\" id=\"udeb8cb38\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u2ef7994a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"hUO14\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如何快速打开、隐蔽大纲</span></h2><p id=\"u8095358b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置好大纲后，大纲会默认呈现固定状态在右侧展示，如果需要隐藏大纲，你可以点击</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635928368130-1b9a16ad-330e-4142-a3a2-cbdcc8217c50.png\" width=\"16.321022033691406\" id=\"tDXdT\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「隐藏大纲」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，这时大纲会收缩在右侧边缘呈现mini状态；如果需要将大纲调出，可以将鼠标轻滑过mini大纲上方，即可展开大纲与你呼应，你点击</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635928532023-09b077ed-fd08-484c-b09c-5751ea95519f.png\" width=\"22.666666666666668\" id=\"vdvEU\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「钉住大纲」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，即可在右侧固定展示。</span></p><p id=\"ucafc8a37\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\"></span></p><p id=\"udca2ebfa\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/gif/21674429/1635824786512-93560b7a-f9e5-4ea5-84ad-fd6a19d7738f.gif\" width=\"1361\" id=\"u8869886a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u23147f51\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u90429b37\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 56639304,
  "title": "如何使用大纲"
}